In our experiment, both relation and class clustering uses SentenceTransformers [reimers-2019-sentence-bert] for embedding cosine similarity computation, with {{arxiv_2411_04920_FO0005||FO}} and global highest threshold {{arxiv_2411_04920_FO0006||FO}} chosen via manual inspection of small held-out sets. For tail predicates, to ensure clustering precision, we set lowest threshold {{arxiv_2411_04920_FO0007||FO}}.